DIGEST
SB 310 Original 2026 Regular Session Cloud
Present law (R.S. 40:31.3) requires the office of public health (OPH) within the La. Dept.
of Health (LDH), to facilitate the establishment of school health centers. Present law requires
centers be registered with OPH. Present law prohibits health centers in schools from
advocating abortion in any way.
Proposed law retains present law and requires LDH, or its designated nonprofit organization,
to produce and distribute signs or posters for school health centers in public high schools and
