to pregnancy information and pregnancy resources listed on the LDH website.
Proposed law defines "designated nonprofit organization" to mean a private, nonprofit
organization that is tax-exempt under the U.S. Internal Revenue Code and that is designated
by the secretary of the LDH to assist the department in furtherance of the provisions of
proposed law.
Proposed law requires the signs to read "Pregnant? Help Is Available for You and Your
Baby!". Proposed law requires signs to be at least 16 inches by 20 inches and the text to be
printed in a large, easily readable font.
Effective upon signature of the governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
